# The reference/ URL namespace was flattened to the site root (2026-06):
# /reference/handbook/01-getting-started/ → /handbook/01-getting-started/.
# Permanently redirect the old paths so existing inbound links and indexed
# search results keep resolving. The :splat captures the rest of the path.
# Cloudflare evaluates these top-to-bottom; the JA rules precede the EN ones
# (they are disjoint, but specific-first keeps intent clear).
/ja/reference/*  /ja/:splat  301
/ja/reference    /ja/        301
/reference/*     /:splat     301
/reference       /           301
